- Purpose: Node implementation of the Web Canvas API backed by Cairo for raster and PDF/SVG output.
- Key factory and methods:
  - createCanvas(width: number, height: number, type?: 'PDF'|'SVG') => Canvas
  - createImageData(width, height) => ImageData
  - loadImage(src: string|Buffer) => Promise<Image>
  - registerFont(path: string, {family: string, weight?: string, style?: string}) => void
  - deregisterAllFonts() => void
  - Canvas#toBuffer(mimeType?: string, config?: any) => Buffer | void with callback
  - Canvas#createPNGStream(config?) => ReadableStream
  - Canvas#createJPEGStream(config?) => ReadableStream
  - Canvas#createPDFStream(config?) => ReadableStream
  - Canvas#toDataURL(type?, quality?) => string
- toBuffer mime types and config payloads:
  - image/png: {compressionLevel, filters, palette?, backgroundIndex?, resolution?}
  - image/jpeg: {quality: 0..1, progressive?: boolean, chromaSubsampling?: boolean}
  - application/pdf: {title, author, subject, keywords, creator, creationDate, modDate}
