IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLISTS & TROUBLESHOOTING

- Expression parsing errors:
  - If evaluation throws on missing variables, validate variable map keys exist before calling evaluate; provide default values via scope or wrapper.
  - For large expressions, pre-parse and reuse AST; benchmark parse vs evaluate overhead.

- Sharp image artifacts and performance:
  - If colorspace or ICC profile looks wrong, inspect input profile and call .withMetadata({ icc: true }) or .toColourspace('srgb').
  - For memory spikes, reduce concurrency via sharp.concurrency() and enable caching limits sharp.cache({memory:..., files:..., items:...}).

- node-canvas installation failures:
  - Missing Cairo/Pango dependencies on Linux: install libcairo2-dev, libpango1.0-dev, libjpeg-dev, libgif-dev, librsvg2-dev.
  - On macOS, ensure Xcode command line tools are installed: xcode-select --install.

- CSV import/export issues:
  - If consumers expect LF only, provide option to normalize line endings and document header presence; always escape quotes by doubling them.

